</span><span class="font-serif italic text-foreground/70">
</span></figcaption></figure><ul class="grid gap-px bg-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border md:grid-cols-3"><li class="bg-background p-8 flex flex-col gap-4"><div class="flex items-baseline justify-between"><span class="font-display text-xs text-coral">0<!-- -->1</span><span class="eyebrow">ARTIST</span></div><h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-coral">Barbara Miklas</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">3D &amp; 2D Artist</p><dl class="mt-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 border-t border-border pt-4"><div><dt class="eyebrow">Experience</dt><dd class="mt-1 font-display text-lg text-foreground">+10y</dd></div><div><dt class="eyebrow">Shipped</dt><dd class="mt-1 font-display text-lg text-foreground">8<!-- --> titles</dd></div></dl></li><li class="bg-background p-8 flex flex-col gap-4"><div class="flex items-baseline justify-between"><span class="font-display text-xs text-coral">0<!-- -->2</span><span class="eyebrow">DEVELOPER</span></div><h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-coral">Paweł Niezabitowski</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Designer · Programmer</p><dl class="mt-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 border-t border-border pt-4"><div><dt class="eyebrow">Experience</dt><dd class="mt-1 font-display text-lg text-foreground">+15y</dd></div><div><dt class="eyebrow">Shipped</dt><dd class="mt-1 font-display text-lg text-foreground">8<!-- --> titles</dd></div></dl></li><li class="bg-background p-8 flex flex-col gap-4"><div class="flex items-baseline justify-between"><span class="font-display text-xs text-coral">0<!-- -->3</span><span class="eyebrow">SCRIPTER</span></div><h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-coral">Bartosz Stachura</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Level Designer · Scripter</p><dl class="mt-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 border-t border-border pt-4"><div><dt class="eyebrow">Experience</dt><dd class="mt-1 font-display text-lg text-foreground">+10y</dd></div><div><dt class="eyebrow">Shipped</dt><dd class="mt-1 font-display text-lg text-foreground">8<!-- --> titles</dd></div></dl></li></ul></div></section><section id="consulting" class="mx-auto max-w-[1320px] px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-28"><div class="mb-12 grid gap-4 border-t border-border pt-6 md:grid-cols-12"><div class="md:col-span-3"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="font-display text-sm text-coral">05</span><span class="eyebrow">GAME CONSULTING</span></div></div><div class="md:col-span-9"><h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(1.9rem,4.5vw,3.25rem)] font-semibold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.02em] text-balance">We also help other studios ship better games.</h2></div></div><div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-12"><div class="md:col-span-5 space-y-5 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed"><p>Unlock Your Game&#x27;s Potential with Mezumo.</p><p>At Mezumo, we provide expert game consulting services to help developers turn their visions into reality. Whether you&#x27;re an indie developer or an established studio, we tailor our insights to meet your unique needs, ensuring your game stands out in a competitive market.<!-- --> <!-- -->Partner with us, and let&#x27;s create something extraordinary together.</p><a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-mint px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-background hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform">Start a conversation <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></a></div><ul class="md:col-span-7 grid gap-px bg-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border"><li class="bg-background p-6"><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Game Design Reviews</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Mechanics, loops, balance, fun-finding.</p></li><li class="bg-background p-6"><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Prototype to Vertical Slice</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">From concept to playable, with you.</p></li></ul></div></section><section class="border-y border-border bg-surface-2 grain"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[1320px] px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-28"><div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 items-end"><h2 class="lg:col-span-8 font-display text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem)] font-semibold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.02em] text-balance">Come hang out in our Discord.<!-- --> <span class="text-muted-foreground">Share strategies, send memes, watch us break our own game in real-time.</span></h2><div class="lg:col-span-4 flex lg:justify-end"><a href="https://discord.gg/phYj8yzg68" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-coral px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-primary-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform">Join the Discord <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="size-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section></main><footer id="contact" class="mx-auto max-w-[1320px] px-6 py-16 lg:px-10 lg:py-20"><div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12"><div class="md:col-span-5"><a href="#top" aria-label="Mezumo — home" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-foreground "><img src="/__l5e/assets-v1/d5eb544a-a1a7-470c-ae98-36898bb63b27/mezumo-mark.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="h-7 w-auto shrink-0"/><span class="font-display text-[1.05rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] leading-none">Mezumo</span></a><p class="mt-6 max-w-sm text-sm text-muted-foreground">A small indie game studio from Kraków, Poland. We make games we&#x27;d want to play.</p><a href="mailto:contact@mezumo.com" class="mt-8 inline-block font-display text-2xl tracking-tight underline decoration-coral decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-coral">contact@mezumo.com</a></div><div class="md:col-span-3"><span class="eyebrow">Studio</span><address class="mt-3 not-italic text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">MEZUMO Sp. z o. o.<br/>Mogilska 43<br/>31-545 Kraków<br/>Poland (PL)<br/><span class="text-xs">NIP: 6783207334</span></address></div><div class="md:col-span-4"><span class="eyebrow">Find us</span><ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm"><li><a href="https://discord.gg/phYj8yzg68" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-foreground hover:text-coral">Discord<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="size-3 opacity-50 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:opacity-100" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/MezumoGames" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-foreground hover:text-coral">Twitter / X<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="size-3 opacity-50 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:opacity-100" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@mezumogames" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-foreground hover:text-coral">TikTok<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="size-3 opacity-50 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:opacity-100" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2366290/Ants_in_Space/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-foreground hover:text-coral">Steam - Ants in Space<svg viewBox="0 0 2